OL,3,CPeacemaker told killer to stop
OL,4,Cfighting before fatal punch
OL,6,FA "peacemaker" was heard saying "stop
OL,7,Ffighting" to his killer, outside a
OL,8,FChichester pub, his last words before
OL,9,Fhe was struck with a fatal punch to
OL,10,Fthe head, a court has heard.
OL,12,FDavid Hallatt, 57, died from blunt
OL,13,Fforce head injury as he fell from the
OL,14,F"dreadful" blow on June 20, 2024.
OL,16,FA trial at Hove Crown Court heard the
OL,17,Ftiler, from Sheffield, South
OL,18,FYorkshire, had "done nothing wrong"
OL,19,Fwhen he was at the Dolphin and Anchor
OL,20,Fpub in Chichester, West Sussex.
