OL,3,CPeacemaker told killer to stop
OL,4,Cfighting before fatal punch
OL,6,FHe tried to stop fighting between a
OL,7,F"troublemaker friend" and other men at
OL,8,Fthe pub.
OL,10,FKieran Egan, 30, of Baldmoor Lake
OL,11,FRoad, Birmingham, has admitted the
OL,12,Fmanslaughter of Mr Hallatt, as he
OL,13,Fdealt the punch to the face, but
OL,14,Fdenies murder and intending to cause
OL,15,Fhim really serious harm.
OL,17,FDyce Barnfield, 31, of Kingstanding
OL,18,FRoad, Birmingham, is jointly charged
OL,19,Fwith his murder, accused of assisting
OL,20,Fand encouraging Egan.
