OL,3,CPeacemaker told killer to stop
OL,4,Cfighting before fatal punch
OL,6,FJurors watched CCTV played in court of
OL,7,Fthe moments leading up to Mr Hallatt's
OL,8,Fdeath, in which Egan is seen trying to
OL,9,Fstamp on Mr Hallatt's friend, before
OL,10,Fturning to Mr Hallatt, standing next
OL,11,Fto him, and striking him in the face.
OL,13,FOpening the case, prosecutor John
OL,14,FPrice KC said: "Mr Hallatt died where
OL,15,Fhe fell, he never recovered
OL,16,Fconsciousness."
