OL,3,CPeacemaker told killer to stop
OL,4,Cfighting before fatal punch
OL,6,F"Following the blow that struck him in
OL,7,Fthe face, the back of his head struck
OL,8,Fthe ground with great force,
OL,9,Ffracturing his skull and causing
OL,10,Fmassive damage to his brain."
OL,12,FHe added: "David Hallatt was four days
OL,13,Fshort of his 58th birthday when he
OL,14,Fdied as a result of a gratuitous act
OL,15,Fof violence."
OL,17,F"It needs to be said at once, Mr
OL,18,FHallatt did nothing wrong that night.
OL,19,FHe was a peacemaker."
